p: $game_map.need_refresh=true
\rI... don't know what to do.
\rHe's gone power-mad.
\rYou're the Augur, right? You have experience with this kind of thing.
\rBut... I'm not sure even you can take him on alone.
\rNot when he has so many powerful Delta legendary Pokemon.
\rBut...
\rOkay. You're the Augur. I can tell you this.
\rWe didn't come to the region to study Deltas. That was all a cover- although, we're definitely happy to be doing that now.
\rOur organization was sponsored by the Second Augur, Jaern.
\rYou know, before he was outed as a cult leader.
\rHis crystal was reacting to something in the far north, at the peak of the mountain, and he wanted us to find it.
\rHe said it was something that would make him powerful beyond his wildest dreams.
\rAfter he was outed as the leader of the Sky Cult, we sealed that area off.
\rIf that filthy traitor was getting involved... well, we didn't want to know.
\rBut now that we've seen the legendary golems in this region as well as their Delta counterparts...
\rWell, let's just say I have a hunch as to what Jaern might have found.
\rIf I'm right, hopefully it can help you out.
\rWell, yeah! Help you out! You have to stop him.
\rThis is why we called you here! You're the Augur now, these are the baddies you have to defend against.
\rListen, if you head to Settlement Juliet, I can radio the guards to let you to the peak.
\rI'll call ahead, tell the guards to let you through.
\rWhatever's up there... it might be our only chance at taking Maple down.
\rAnd I should say... Maple's not as smart as he thinks he is if he thinks that we don't have Master Balls too.
Kernel.pbReceiveItem(PBItems::MASTERBALL)
\rUse that. Hopefully it helps.
\rAnd be careful- as soon as you find what's up there... well, I'm sure Maple won't be too far behind.
\rYou're our best hope.
$game_map.need_refresh=true
A
<turtwig>
pbWildBattle(PBSpecies::DELTAREGICE,100)
A
